context:
KR:
&lt;왜 이 자들의 모습이…&gt;
EN:
&lt;What’s going on with them…?&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;다행히 부분적으로는 스스로 검열통제를 할 수 있나 보군.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Good. It appears that I can censor these with my own will, at least to a degree.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;자네들의 목표는 뒤틀림 분류와 심상던전의 끝까지 도달하여 나를 원래대로 돌려놓는 것이라네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Your mission here is to classify my Distortion, reach the end of this Dungeon of the Fathoms, and bring me back.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;과거를 파헤치는 것이 아니라.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Your mission, however, does <i>not</i> involve digging into my past.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;아마 정상적인 소통을 하긴 어려울 걸세. 심상던전이니.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;I don’t believe any level of proper communication will be feasible, given that you are in a Dungeon of the Fathoms.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;미안하지만 그게 가능했다면 여기를 보다 흥미로운 공간으로 만들었을 걸세. 가령 모든 책이 다 존재한다고 하였던 그 도서관의 모습이라던가…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;I regret to tell you that the setting of this Dungeon is out of my hands. Had it been up to me, I would have manifested a place that was much more fascinating than this. Like that Library, fabled to have every book in existence…&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;이젠 지나간 커리어 중 하나지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;One of my past careers, yes.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;어쩔 수 없지. 싸우는 수밖에…&gt;
EN:
&lt;It can't be helped. Let's get ready for a fight...&gt;
